skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: v. interview
Developer Terms of Use
des:
This skill will let vinterview users know about their upcoming live interviews and self taken assessments that need to be reviewed in the next 24 hours.
To get started, link your account and use the phrase : 

Use these phrases given below to know about the number of total interviews you have including upcoming live interviews and self taken assessments that needs to be reviewed.

Alexa ask vinterview what does my schedule look like today ? 

OR

Alexa ask vinterview How many interviews have been assigned to me in total


To know you all upcoming live interviews in next 24 hours use the below phrase:

Alexa ask vinterview to tell me about my scheduled live interviews

OR

Alexa ask vinterview about my scheduled live interviews



To know you all self taken assessments in next 24 hours use the below phrase:

Alexa ask vinterview How many self taken assessments have been assigned to me

OR

Alexa ask vinterview tell me about the number of self taken assessments
